reviewText: Very poor acting. The actress playing Alaina, besides lacking any discernible acting skills, has a terribly grating voice. I gave up on this movie about half-way through. Besides the poor acting, it was boring. (I particularly grew tired of repetitive scenes of Alaina & her mother flailing around in hospital beds).
Thought this was good. I liked it. But what is she gonna do about Sage Hawthorne buried in her backyard?? Lol!
The acting was so horrible that I could only make it through 15 minutes before quitting.
Amazing Kelsey! Loved it from start to finish, well done! Laura was excellent also! Great story line...Within These Walls gets
If you're into the indie horror scene..definitely check this movie out.
Within These Walls is incredible. Dark, suspencful, and keeps you at the edge of your seat. Highly recommend it!
